      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline remains reliable. The suspension retains its precision with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the legendary handling characteristics of this M-chassis. Mechanically sound and ready for the apex.",
