      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition, perfect for a driver who values both performance and aesthetics. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though closer inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper\u2014honest evidence of its time on the road. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple with no major wear, and every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, operates with factory-spec precision. Mechanically, the car is robust, featuring a full service history, recent fluid flushes, and tires with excellent tread life remaining. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers the quiet, composed ride of a vehicle that has been truly cared for. This is a complete, turn-key package for a discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality car.",
